text:
Hehe...
I'm glad the fans enjoyed it...

Ah...!
That was a great performance.
It's reassuring to hear you say that.

Wearing this costume and dancing, I had so much fun...
It felt like I was diving into the world of the song...

The lights dancing softly, swaying gently...
And the penlights waving...

Ah, I...
I'm glad I became an idol...

Yeah, I get it...
It somehow comes across.

For the encore too...
I'll give it my all, Producer-san...!
Ah, show us the next song too, Chiyuki...!!
